@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    /* ===== Reset & Base ===== */
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
        --primary: #2563eb;
        --primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
        --primary-light: #dbeafe;
        --text-dark: #0f172a;
        --text-muted: #64748b;
        --bg-light: #f8fafc;
        --border-radius: 16px;
        --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
        --shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);
        --shadow-lg: 0 16px 40px rgba(15,23,42,0.15);
        --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    html, body {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== Hero Section ===== */
    .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--primary) 50%, #3b82f6 100%);
        padding: 100px 20px;
        color: white;
    }

        .hero::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -40%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30%;
            left: -5%;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

    @@keyframes float {
        0%, 100%

    {
        transform: translateY(0px);
    }

    50% {
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }

    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 60px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

        .hero-text h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #93c5fd, #dbeafe);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

    .hero-text .subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .hero-text .description {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 500px;
    }

    .hero-icon {
        text-align: center;
        perspective: 1000px;
    }

    .icon-circle {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 90px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
    }

    @@keyframes rotate {
        0%

    {
        transform: rotateY(0deg);
    }

    100% {
        transform: rotateY(360deg);
    }

    }

    /* ===== Stats Section ===== */
    .stats-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: -50px auto 0;
        padding: 0 20px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .stat-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 32px 28px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        transition: var(--transition);
        border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
    }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
        }

        .stat-card .number {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #1e40af);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .stat-card .label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

    /* ===== Values Section ===== */
    .values-section {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 100px auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .section-header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

    .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 28px;
    }

    .value-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 40px 32px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        transition: var(--transition);
        border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .value-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #3b82f6);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
        }

            .value-card:hover::before {
                transform: scaleX(1);
            }

    .value-icon {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #bfdbfe);
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 40px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        color: var(--primary);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
        transition: var(--transition);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .value-icon::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s ease;
        }

    .value-card:hover .value-icon {
        transform: scale(1.1) rotateY(10deg);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
    }

        .value-card:hover .value-icon::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

    .value-card h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .value-card p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ===== Story Section ===== */
    .story-section {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 100px auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 60px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .story-content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

        .story-content p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

    .story-image {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

        .story-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .story-image:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .story-image::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1), transparent);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 2;
        }

    /* ===== Team Section ===== */
    .team-section {
        background: white;
        padding: 80px 20px;
        margin: 60px 0;
    }

    .team-content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .team-section .section-header {
        margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .team-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 32px;
    }

    .team-member {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .member-image {
        width: 140px;
        height: 140px;
        background: var(--primary-light);
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 50px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        border: 4px solid white;
        position: relative;
    }

        .member-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .member-image i {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

    .member-name {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .member-role {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .member-bio {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== CTA Section ===== */
    .cta-section {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 100px auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .cta-card {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #1e40af 100%);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 60px 50px;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 40px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .cta-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -5%;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .cta-card::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30%;
            left: -10%;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

    .cta-content {
        flex: 1;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

        .cta-content h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .cta-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

    .cta-button {
        padding: 14px 32px;
        background: white;
        color: var(--primary);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 15px;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        white-space: nowrap;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        transition: var(--transition);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #f0f4ff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .cta-button:active {
            transform: translateY(0px);
        }

    /* ===== Footer Spacing ===== */
    .footer-spacing {
        height: 60px;
    }

    /* ===== Responsive Design ===== */
    @@media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .hero-content

    {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
    }

    .hero-icon {
        display: none;
    }

    .story-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .cta-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero

    {
        padding: 70px 20px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
    }

    .hero-text .subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .section-header h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .value-card {
        padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .cta-content h3 {
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    }

    @@media (max-width: 576px) {
        .hero

    {
        padding: 50px 16px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
    }

    .hero-text .subtitle {
        font-size: 15px;
    }

    .hero-text .description {
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .stats-container {
        margin-top: -30px;
    }

    .stat-card {
        padding: 24px 20px;
    }

        .stat-card .number {
            font-size: 28px;
        }

    .values-grid {
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .value-card {
        padding: 24px 16px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    .story-section {
        margin: 60px auto;
    }

    .cta-section {
        margin: 60px auto;
    }

    .cta-card {
        padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .cta-content h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    }
</style>

<!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>About <span>StayVerse</span></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Effortless Reservations, Powered by AI</p>
            <p class="description">Since day one, we've been on a mission to make booking a table as easy as sending a text — combining real-time availability with a conversational assistant that handles the rest.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-icon">
            <div class="icon-circle">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Stats ===== -->
<div class="stats-container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="number">50K+</div>
            <div class="label">RESERVATIONS BOOKED</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="number">120+</div>
            <div class="label">PARTNER RESTAURANTS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="number">98%</div>
            <div class="label">ON-TIME CONFIRMATION</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="number">24/7</div>
            <div class="label">AI ASSISTANT SUPPORT</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== Values ===== -->
<section class="values-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
        <p>The principles that guide every reservation we power</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M20 2L24.47 13.53H36.53L27.03 20.47L31.5 32L20 25.06L8.5 32L12.97 20.47L3.47 13.53H15.53L20 2Z" fill="currentColor" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Speed & Simplicity</h3>
            <p>No phone calls, no hold music. Check availability and confirm a table in under a minute — it's that straightforward.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M20 2C10.06 2 2 10.06 2 20C2 29.94 10.06 38 20 38C29.94 38 38 29.94 38 20C38 10.06 29.94 2 20 2ZM15 28L6 19L9.07 15.93L15 21.86L30.93 6L34 9.07L15 28Z" fill="currentColor" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Smart Assistance</h3>
            <p>Our AI assistant understands natural requests and books directly into live availability. Just tell us what you need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M20 2C10.06 2 2 10.06 2 20C2 29.94 10.06 38 20 38C29.94 38 38 29.94 38 20C38 10.06 29.94 2 20 2ZM18 28L10 20L12.83 17.17L18 22.34L27.17 13.17L30 16L18 28Z" fill="currentColor" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Reliability You Can Trust</h3>
            <p>Real-time sync with our database means no double bookings and no surprises at the door. Ever.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Story ===== -->
<section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-content">
        <h2>Built for Diners and Restaurants Alike</h2>
        <p>StayVerse started as a simple idea: reservations shouldn't require waiting on hold or guessing whether a table is actually free. We built a system that connects guests directly to live availability, eliminating the guesswork.</p>
        <p>Today, restaurants use StayVerse to manage their floor in real time, while guests enjoy instant confirmations — whether they book through our site or simply chat with our assistant. It's a win-win for everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559339352-11d035aa65de?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=70" alt="Restaurant dining experience" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Team Section ===== -->
<section class="team-section">
    <div class="team-content">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <p>Passionate people building the future of restaurant reservations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="member-image">
